data.description: If you are just starting out or looking to down size this is the home for you. Charming 3 bedroom , 2 full bath ranch located in the Chesaning school district. Large master bedroom with custom tile shower master bathroom that leads into your walk-in closet. Many updates have been completed on this home. Sitting on 1.72 acres backing up to a wooded lot behind you have plenty of space for storage or entertaining. All appliances stay and a 2 car detached garage.
